{"tid":426814,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 19世紀 波斯第一美女","createTime":"2017-10-07T03:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T06:15:44.000Z","uid":145117,"like":621,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"cb34a5ad61a25daabf79f1df512901ec505bf4ee","tid":426814,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"我們先看看現代伊朗女生的外貌：<br />\n<br />\n如果你也到過伊朗旅遊，大概對街上的美人印象頗深刻⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n街頭隨拍－－要注意的是，伊朗跟沙地阿拉伯不同，女生只需要披頭巾，而不必戴面紗。<br />\n五官可以外露，伊朗女生也挺喜歡打扮，除了天生美人胚子；坊間也流行整容，曲尺鼻就是美⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/pgirl05_124302081559d7afd1ba0c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fpgirl05_124302081559d7afd1ba0c6.jpg&h=68c7f91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/pgirl02_167037753059d7afd4c8b05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fpgirl02_167037753059d7afd4c8b05.jpg&h=6e22d5fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/pgirl01_131010637659d7afd6520fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fpgirl01_131010637659d7afd6520fd.jpg&h=ff11d157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">準備穿越到19世紀！<br />\n伊朗「生鬚公主」登場咯！</span><br />\n<br />\n不少人印象中的波斯美女，就像上面的組圖般，高高的鼻、大大的眼，雖然有頭紗長衫包裹，好多時候都是身材高窕的女性，可是這位被奉為「波斯第一美女」的卡扎爾公主，真的令人（拳頭）硬了！她不但長得一副男人相，更有超濃眉和鬍子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/113501_aa723867605f0c0a036e1061c76facbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F113501_aa723867605f0c0a036e1061c76facbf.jpg&h=6d37230c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/113519_90403601008076e5ba4f70499ed7f94e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F113519_90403601008076e5ba4f70499ed7f94e.jpg&h=f9240329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有騙你，她真的是伊朗公主⋯⋯你也沒有看錯，她有鬍子⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/shahandwife04_180551011459d75c3d98bc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fshahandwife04_180551011459d75c3d98bc4.jpg&h=21114709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所謂有其母必有其女，公主之所以長成這樣，多少是因為這位母親<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/113921_c814299cfaec1b8a921f106952f550d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F113921_c814299cfaec1b8a921f106952f550d1.jpg&h=ae817b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女性基因都非常接近，一個餅印！（左邊是皇帝&hellip;.)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波斯人真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1496dd11f8284d11894ffe6dc6c91572435f8e84","tid":426814,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd756543afa2e747be4c16558b26c9ea8099fc0","tid":426814,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"唔點解後黎進化到咁靚，定係淨係波斯公特別樣衰？"},{"pid":"5991c3e0418674de0434f4713a029a73bc61f027","tid":426814,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔點解後黎進化到咁靚，定係淨係波斯公特別樣衰？</blockquote><br />\n可能口味變左 條條女變曬整容臭雞"},{"pid":"b3941bbcc8b623cccd336825e76b69033511d4c7","tid":426814,"uid":33939,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"最尾張圖，左邊是皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c